Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.63,0:21:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\pos(380,700)}和天翼种进行的游戏只有传统的一种
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.00,0:21:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\pos(380,700)}这没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.16,0:21:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\pos(380,700)}是的 如果和文献写的一样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.84,0:21:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\pos(380,700)}那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.52,0:21:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\pos(380,700)}那么从现在起 征服世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.12,0:22:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.25,0:23:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那么 天使大人在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这可不是天使那么善良的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.71,0:23:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这家伙代表着死亡本身
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.32,0:23:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Excuse 那里的Person们 来Me的图书馆有What事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.28,0:23:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}气氛全无
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.07,0:23:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}史蒂芙啊 竟然死了 真丢脸
